<% title 'Assembly is a new way for people around the world to collectively build, launch, and grow startups.' %>
<%= track 'home.viewed' %>

<div class="navbar navbar-default navbar-static-top omega">
  <div class="container-fluid">

    <div class="navbar-header">
      <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#platform-navbar-collapse">
        <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </button>

      <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= root_path %>">
        <span class="icon icon-logo-filled"></span>
        Assembly
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="platform-navbar-collapse">
      <div class="navbar-right">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li>
            <a href="<%= new_user_session_path %>">
              Log in
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="navbar-form">
              <a class="btn btn-success" href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>">Sign up</a>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><!-- .navbar -->

<div class="page page-flat">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">


        <div class="sheet-">
          <h1 class="text-center">
            Build, launch, and grow a startup with talented people around the world
          </h1>

          <br>
          <br>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">

              <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
                <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="//player.vimeo.com/video/102253176" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
              </div>

              <br>
              <br>

            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="row">

            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-large">
              <p>
                <strong>Build a product with others.</strong>
                Startups on Assembly are unlike traditional companies. They don't have investors, shareholders, or even employees. Instead, a global community creates and owns them, together.
              </p>

              <p>
                <strong>Anyone can work on a product.</strong>
                The entire process is a collaborative effort including its vision, development, design and marketing.
              </p>

              <p>
                <strong>Share profit as the products you work on make money.</strong>
                Everyone shares in the success of the startups they help create. Those involved earn App Coins from others in the community for their work. At the end of each month Assembly pays the bills and splits the proceeds amongst everyone with App Coins.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>

          <br>


          <div class="text-center">
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>">
              Start building
            </a>
          </div>

          <br>
          <br>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render 'shared/footer' %>
